{
  "video_id": "6OaIdwUdSxE",
  "title": "Tyler DeWitt: Hey science teachers -- make it fun",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Morton Bast Reviewer: Krystian Aparta"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16219.000000000002,
      "end_time": 17656.0,
      "text": "Let me tell you a story."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18228.0,
      "end_time": 21975.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s my first year as a new high school science teacher,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21999.0,
      "end_time": 23294.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m so eager."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23787.0,
      "end_time": 27794.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m so excited, I&#39;m pouring myself into my lesson plans."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28953.0,
      "end_time": 33786.0,
      "text": "But I&#39;m slowly coming to this horrifying realization"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 33810.0,
      "end_time": 37341.0,
      "text": "that my students just might not be learning anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 38865.0,
      "end_time": 40572.0,
      "text": "This happens one day:"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 40596.0,
      "end_time": 43730.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d just assigned my class to read this textbook chapter"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 43754.0,
      "end_time": 46803.0,
      "text": "about my favorite subject in all of biology:"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 47495.0,
      "end_time": 50177.0,
      "text": "viruses and how they attack."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 50987.0,
      "end_time": 53315.0,
      "text": "And so I&#39;m so excited to discuss this with them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 53339.0,
      "end_time": 56686.0,
      "text": "and I come in and I say, \"Can somebody please explain"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 56710.0,
      "end_time": 59805.0,
      "text": "the main ideas and why this is so cool?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 61720.0,
      "end_time": 62247.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s silence."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 64611.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67571.0,
      "text": "Finally, my favorite student, she looks me straight in the eye,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 67596.0,
      "end_time": 70144.0,
      "text": "and she says, \"The reading sucked.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 70517.0,
      "end_time": 71969.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 72785.0,
      "end_time": 74800.0,
      "text": "And then she clarified."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 74104.0,
      "end_time": 76603.0,
      "text": "She said, \"You know what, I don&#39;t mean that it sucks."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 76627.0,
      "end_time": 78664.0,
      "text": "I mean I didn&#39;t understand a word of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 78689.0,
      "end_time": 82252.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s boring, who cares, and it sucks.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 82713.0,
      "end_time": 84568.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 84593.0,
      "end_time": 89459.0,
      "text": "These sympathetic smiles spread all throughout the room now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 89483.0,
      "end_time": 94292.0,
      "text": "and I realize that all of my other students are in the same boat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 94316.0,
      "end_time": 98204.0,
      "text": "that maybe they took notes or memorized definitions from the textbook,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 98228.0,
      "end_time": 103306.0,
      "text": "but not one of them really understood the main ideas."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 103331.0,
      "end_time": 105981.0,
      "text": "Not one of them can tell me why this stuff is so cool,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 106500.0,
      "end_time": 107338.0,
      "text": "why it&#39;s so important."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 109497.0,
      "end_time": 111417.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m totally clueless."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 111441.0,
      "end_time": 114360.0,
      "text": "I have no idea what to do next."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 114711.0,
      "end_time": 117623.0,
      "text": "So the only thing I can think of is say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 117647.0,
      "end_time": 120337.0,
      "text": "\"Listen. Let me tell you a story."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 121566.0,
      "end_time": 127591.0,
      "text": "The main characters in the story are bacteria and viruses."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 127615.0,
      "end_time": 130417.0,
      "text": "These guys are blown up a couple million times."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 131910.0,
      "end_time": 134233.0,
      "text": "The real bacteria and viruses are so small"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 134257.0,
      "end_time": 136511.0,
      "text": "we can&#39;t see them without a microscope,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 136535.0,
      "end_time": 138645.0,
      "text": "and you guys might know bacteria and viruses"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 138669.0,
      "end_time": 140233.0,
      "text": "because they both make us sick."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 140796.0,
      "end_time": 142691.0,
      "text": "But what a lot of people don&#39;t know"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 142716.0,
      "end_time": 146478.0,
      "text": "is that viruses can also make bacteria sick.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 147319.0,
      "end_time": 149795.0,
      "text": "Now, the story that I start telling my kids,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 149819.0,
      "end_time": 152905.0,
      "text": "it starts out like a horror story."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 154147.0,
      "end_time": 157140.0,
      "text": "Once upon a time, there&#39;s this happy little bacterium."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 157750.0,
      "end_time": 159217.0,
      "text": "Don&#39;t get too attached to him."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 159241.0,
      "end_time": 160933.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 160957.0,
      "end_time": 163623.0,
      "text": "Maybe he&#39;s floating around in your stomach"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 163647.0,
      "end_time": 165821.0,
      "text": "or in some spoiled food somewhere,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 165845.0,
      "end_time": 169449.0,
      "text": "and all of a sudden, he starts to not feel so good."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 169473.0,
      "end_time": 172510.0,
      "text": "Maybe he ate something bad for lunch."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 172750.0,
      "end_time": 174613.0,
      "text": "And then things get really horrible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 174638.0,
      "end_time": 176235.0,
      "text": "as his skin rips apart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 176259.0,
      "end_time": 179753.0,
      "text": "and he sees a virus coming out from his insides."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 180765.0,
      "end_time": 184310.0,
      "text": "And then it gets horrible when he bursts open"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 184335.0,
      "end_time": 188580.0,
      "text": "and an army of viruses floods out from his insides."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 189896.0,
      "end_time": 191833.0,
      "text": "\"Ouch\" is right."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 192903.0,
      "end_time": 195427.0,
      "text": "If you see this, and you&#39;re a bacterium,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 195451.0,
      "end_time": 198265.0,
      "text": "this is like your worst nightmare."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 198673.0,
      "end_time": 201290.0,
      "text": "But if you&#39;re a virus and you see this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 201530.0,
      "end_time": 204690.0,
      "text": "you cross those little legs of yours and you think,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 204930.0,
      "end_time": 205600.0,
      "text": "\"We rock.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 205989.0,
      "end_time": 210346.0,
      "text": "Because it took a lot of crafty work to infect this bacterium."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 211430.0,
      "end_time": 212676.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s what had to happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 213247.0,
      "end_time": 216429.0,
      "text": "A virus grabbed onto a bacterium"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 216453.0,
      "end_time": 218961.0,
      "text": "and it slipped its DNA into it."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 220630.0,
      "end_time": 223420.0,
      "text": "The next thing is that virus DNA made stuff"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 223444.0,
      "end_time": 226428.0,
      "text": "that chopped up the bacteria DNA."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 227705.0,
      "end_time": 230141.0,
      "text": "And now that we&#39;ve gotten rid of the bacteria DNA,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 230165.0,
      "end_time": 233970.0,
      "text": "the virus DNA takes control of the cell"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 233994.0,
      "end_time": 237470.0,
      "text": "and it tells it to start making more viruses."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 238613.0,
      "end_time": 241795.0,
      "text": "Because, you see, DNA is like a blueprint"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 241819.0,
      "end_time": 244167.0,
      "text": "that tells living things what to make."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 245423.0,
      "end_time": 248803.0,
      "text": "So this is kind of like going into a car factory"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 248827.0,
      "end_time": 253779.0,
      "text": "and replacing the blueprints with blueprints for killer robots."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 254525.0,
      "end_time": 257469.0,
      "text": "The workers still come the next day, they do their job,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 257493.0,
      "end_time": 260550.0,
      "text": "but they&#39;re following different instructions."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 260784.0,
      "end_time": 264537.0,
      "text": "So replacing the bacteria DNA with virus DNA"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 264561.0,
      "end_time": 269383.0,
      "text": "turns the bacteria into a factory for making viruses --"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 269407.0,
      "end_time": 273161.0,
      "text": "that is, until it&#39;s so filled with viruses that it bursts."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 274156.0,
      "end_time": 277536.0,
      "text": "But that&#39;s not the only way that viruses infect bacteria."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 278850.0,
      "end_time": 281543.0,
      "text": "Some are much more crafty."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 281567.0,
      "end_time": 282717.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 284251.0,
      "end_time": 289360.0,
      "text": "When a secret agent virus infects a bacterium,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 289600.0,
      "end_time": 290822.0,
      "text": "they do a little espionage."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 291495.0,
      "end_time": 295596.0,
      "text": "Here, this cloaked, secret agent virus"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 295620.0,
      "end_time": 298383.0,
      "text": "is slipping his DNA into the bacterial cell,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 298407.0,
      "end_time": 300200.0,
      "text": "but here&#39;s the kicker:"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 300260.0,
      "end_time": 303899.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t do anything harmful -- not at first."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 304303.0,
      "end_time": 309858.0,
      "text": "Instead, it silently slips into the bacteria&#39;s own DNA,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 309882.0,
      "end_time": 314580.0,
      "text": "and it just stays there like a terrorist sleeper cell,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 314604.0,
      "end_time": 316728.0,
      "text": "waiting for instructions."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 317474.0,
      "end_time": 323171.0,
      "text": "And what&#39;s interesting about this is now, whenever this bacteria has babies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 323196.0,
      "end_time": 328315.0,
      "text": "the babies also have the virus DNA in them."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 329130.0,
      "end_time": 332846.0,
      "text": "So now we have a whole extended bacteria family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 332870.0,
      "end_time": 335671.0,
      "text": "filled with virus sleeper cells."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 336366.0,
      "end_time": 341111.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re just happily living together until a signal happens"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 341135.0,
      "end_time": 345579.0,
      "text": "and bam! -- all of the DNA pops out."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 345603.0,
      "end_time": 349245.0,
      "text": "It takes control of these cells, turns them into virus-making factories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 349269.0,
      "end_time": 351610.0,
      "text": "and they all burst,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 351850.0,
      "end_time": 353782.0,
      "text": "a huge, extended bacteria family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 353807.0,
      "end_time": 356928.0,
      "text": "all dying with viruses spilling out of their guts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 356952.0,
      "end_time": 359944.0,
      "text": "the viruses taking over the bacterium."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 361920.0,
      "end_time": 365491.0,
      "text": "So now you understand how viruses can attack cells."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 366150.0,
      "end_time": 367619.0,
      "text": "There are two ways:"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 367643.0,
      "end_time": 370602.0,
      "text": "On the left is what we call the lytic way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 370626.0,
      "end_time": 373935.0,
      "text": "where the viruses go right in and take over the cells."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 374538.0,
      "end_time": 377609.0,
      "text": "On the [right] is the lysogenic way"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 377633.0,
      "end_time": 380200.0,
      "text": "that uses secret agent viruses."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 381204.0,
      "end_time": 383458.0,
      "text": "So this stuff is not that hard, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 383482.0,
      "end_time": 385481.0,
      "text": "And now all of you understand it."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 385505.0,
      "end_time": 387496.0,
      "text": "But if you&#39;ve graduated from high school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 387520.0,
      "end_time": 390306.0,
      "text": "I can almost guarantee you&#39;ve seen this information before."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 390806.0,
      "end_time": 395813.0,
      "text": "But I bet it was presented in a way that it didn&#39;t exactly stick in your mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 397379.0,
      "end_time": 400847.0,
      "text": "So when my students were first learning this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 400871.0,
      "end_time": 402609.0,
      "text": "why did they hate it so much?"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 403212.0,
      "end_time": 405346.0,
      "text": "Well, there were a couple of reasons."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 405370.0,
      "end_time": 407521.0,
      "text": "First of all, I can guarantee you"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 407545.0,
      "end_time": 410927.0,
      "text": "you that their textbooks didn&#39;t have secret agent viruses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 410951.0,
      "end_time": 413417.0,
      "text": "and they didn&#39;t have horror stories."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 413940.0,
      "end_time": 416646.0,
      "text": "You know, in the communication of science,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 416670.0,
      "end_time": 420694.0,
      "text": "there is this obsession with seriousness."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 420718.0,
      "end_time": 422820.0,
      "text": "It kills me. I&#39;m not kidding."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 422844.0,
      "end_time": 425730.0,
      "text": "I used to work for an educational publisher,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 425970.0,
      "end_time": 428756.0,
      "text": "and as a writer, I was always told never to use stories"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 428780.0,
      "end_time": 430667.0,
      "text": "or fun, engaging language,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 430692.0,
      "end_time": 435660.0,
      "text": "because then my work might not be viewed as \"serious\" and \"scientific.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 436108.0,
      "end_time": 439179.0,
      "text": "I mean, because God forbid somebody have fun"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 439203.0,
      "end_time": 440970.0,
      "text": "when they&#39;re learning science."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 440995.0,
      "end_time": 445833.0,
      "text": "So we have this field of science that&#39;s all about slime"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 445857.0,
      "end_time": 448200.0,
      "text": "and color changes."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 448224.0,
      "end_time": 449428.0,
      "text": "Check this out."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 459756.0,
      "end_time": 463517.0,
      "text": "And then we have, of course, as any good scientist has to have ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 464375.0,
      "end_time": 465732.0,
      "text": "explosions!"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 467163.0,
      "end_time": 471829.0,
      "text": "But if a textbook seems too much fun,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 471853.0,
      "end_time": 474449.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s somehow unscientific."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 475771.0,
      "end_time": 478574.0,
      "text": "Now another problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 478598.0,
      "end_time": 484430.0,
      "text": "was that the language in their textbook was truly incomprehensible."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 484978.0,
      "end_time": 487763.0,
      "text": "If we want to summarize that story that I told you earlier,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 487787.0,
      "end_time": 489730.0,
      "text": "we could start by saying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 489970.0,
      "end_time": 491239.0,
      "text": "\"These viruses make copies of themselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 491263.0,
      "end_time": 493597.0,
      "text": "by slipping their DNA into a bacterium.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 494263.0,
      "end_time": 497604.0,
      "text": "The way this showed up in the textbook, it looked like this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 497628.0,
      "end_time": 500842.0,
      "text": "\"Bacteriophage replication is initiated"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 500866.0,
      "end_time": 505508.0,
      "text": "through the introduction of viral nucleic acid into a bacterium.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 506225.0,
      "end_time": 510296.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s great, perfect for 13-year-olds."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 511312.0,
      "end_time": 512493.0,
      "text": "But here&#39;s the thing:"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 512517.00000000006,
      "end_time": 515670.00000000006,
      "text": "There are plenty of people in science education"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 515909.99999999994,
      "end_time": 517245.99999999994,
      "text": "who would look at this and say there&#39;s no way"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 517270.0,
      "end_time": 519688.0,
      "text": "that we could ever give that to students,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 519712.0,
      "end_time": 524164.0,
      "text": "because it contains some language that isn&#39;t completely accurate."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 524926.0,
      "end_time": 527759.0,
      "text": "For example, I told you that viruses have DNA."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 527783.0,
      "end_time": 530386.0,
      "text": "Well, a very tiny fraction of them don&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 530410.0,
      "end_time": 532353.0,
      "text": "They have something called RNA instead."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 532725.0,
      "end_time": 536270.0,
      "text": "So a professional science writer would say, \"That has to go."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 536510.0,
      "end_time": 538641.0,
      "text": "We have to change it to something much more technical.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 538665.0,
      "end_time": 541392.0,
      "text": "And after a team of professional science editors"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 541417.0,
      "end_time": 545226.0,
      "text": "went over this really simple explanation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 545250.0,
      "end_time": 549654.0,
      "text": "they&#39;d find fault with almost every word I&#39;ve used,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 549678.0,
      "end_time": 552583.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;d have to change anything that wasn&#39;t serious enough,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 552607.0,
      "end_time": 554322.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;d have to change everything"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 554346.0,
      "end_time": 556828.0,
      "text": "that wasn&#39;t 100 percent perfect."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 557804.0,
      "end_time": 559668.0,
      "text": "Then it would be accurate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 559692.0,
      "end_time": 564650.0,
      "text": "but it would be completely impossible to understand."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 564565.0,
      "end_time": 566263.0,
      "text": "This is horrifying."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 566813.0,
      "end_time": 571682.0,
      "text": "You know, I keep talking about this idea of telling a story,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 571706.0,
      "end_time": 576277.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s like science communication has taken on this idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 576301.0,
      "end_time": 579356.0,
      "text": "of what I call the tyranny of precision,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 579380.0,
      "end_time": 581511.0,
      "text": "where you can&#39;t just tell a story."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 581535.0,
      "end_time": 587153.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s like science has become that horrible storyteller that we all know"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 587177.0,
      "end_time": 589772.0,
      "text": "who gives us all the details nobody cares about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 589796.0,
      "end_time": 593621.0,
      "text": "where you&#39;re like, \"Oh, I met my friend for lunch the other day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 593645.0,
      "end_time": 595438.0,
      "text": "and she was wearing these ugly jeans."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 595462.0,
      "end_time": 598462.0,
      "text": "I mean, they weren&#39;t really jeans, they were more like leggings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 598486.0,
      "end_time": 601120.0,
      "text": "but I guess they&#39;re actually kind of more like jeggings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 601144.0,
      "end_time": 605457.0,
      "text": "and you&#39;re just like, \"Oh my God. What is the point?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 606360.0,
      "end_time": 609996.0,
      "text": "Or even worse, science education is becoming"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 610200.0,
      "end_time": 613200.0,
      "text": "like that guy who always says, \"Actually.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 613995.0,
      "end_time": 615851.0,
      "text": "You want to be like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 615875.0,
      "end_time": 618986.0,
      "text": "\"Oh, dude, we had to get up in the middle of the night"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 619100.0,
      "end_time": 621692.0,
      "text": "and drive a hundred miles in total darkness.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 621716.0,
      "end_time": 626374.0,
      "text": "And that guy&#39;s like, \"Actually, it was 87.3 miles.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 626398.0,
      "end_time": 630763.0,
      "text": "And you&#39;re like, \"Actually, shut up! I&#39;m just trying to tell a story.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 633731.0,
      "end_time": 638540.0,
      "text": "Because good storytelling is all about emotional connection."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 639270.0,
      "end_time": 641797.0,
      "text": "We have to convince our audience"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 641821.0,
      "end_time": 644820.0,
      "text": "that what we&#39;re talking about matters."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 644805.0,
      "end_time": 650360.0,
      "text": "But just as important is knowing which details we should leave out"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 650600.0,
      "end_time": 652689.0,
      "text": "so that the main point still comes across."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 653539.0,
      "end_time": 656521.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m reminded of what the architect Mies van der Rohe said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 656546.0,
      "end_time": 659911.0,
      "text": "and I paraphrase, when he said that sometimes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 659935.0,
      "end_time": 662863.0,
      "text": "you have to lie in order to tell the truth."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 663498.0,
      "end_time": 668130.0,
      "text": "I think this sentiment is particularly relevant to science education."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 670212.0,
      "end_time": 676978.0,
      "text": "Now, finally, I am often so disappointed"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 677200.0,
      "end_time": 681549.0,
      "text": "when people think that I&#39;m advocating a dumbing down of science."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 682208.0,
      "end_time": 683358.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s not true at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 683906.0,
      "end_time": 686683.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m currently a Ph.D. student at MIT,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 686707.0,
      "end_time": 691689.0,
      "text": "and I absolutely understand the importance of detailed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 691713.0,
      "end_time": 696582.0,
      "text": "specific scientific communication between experts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 696606.0,
      "end_time": 700340.0,
      "text": "but not when we&#39;re trying to teach 13-year-olds."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 701116.0,
      "end_time": 706188.0,
      "text": "If a young learner thinks that all viruses have DNA,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 706212.0,
      "end_time": 710242.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s not going to ruin their chances of success in science."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 711726.0,
      "end_time": 715281.0,
      "text": "But if a young learner can&#39;t understand anything in science"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 715305.0,
      "end_time": 719239.0,
      "text": "and learns to hate it because it all sounds like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 719264.0,
      "end_time": 722233.0,
      "text": "that will ruin their chances of success."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 724250.0,
      "end_time": 725331.0,
      "text": "This needs to stop ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 726378.0,
      "end_time": 730172.0,
      "text": "and I wish that the change could come from the institutions at the top"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 730196.0,
      "end_time": 731958.0,
      "text": "that are perpetuating these problems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 731982.0,
      "end_time": 735401.0,
      "text": "and I beg them, I beseech them to just stop it."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 736788.0,
      "end_time": 738293.0,
      "text": "But I think that&#39;s unlikely."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 738769.0,
      "end_time": 742308.0,
      "text": "So we are so lucky that we have resources"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 742332.0,
      "end_time": 745466.0,
      "text": "like the Internet, where we can circumvent these institutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 745490.0,
      "end_time": 747546.0,
      "text": "from the bottom up."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 748853.0,
      "end_time": 751741.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a growing number of online resources"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 751765.0,
      "end_time": 755670.0,
      "text": "that are dedicated to just explaining science"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 755910.0,
      "end_time": 757757.0,
      "text": "in simple, understandable ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 758194.0,
      "end_time": 760550.0,
      "text": "I dream of a Wikipedia-like website"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 760574.0,
      "end_time": 764272.0,
      "text": "that would explain any scientific concept you can think of"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 764297.0,
      "end_time": 767908.0,
      "text": "in simple language any middle schooler can understand."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 768781.0,
      "end_time": 772224.0,
      "text": "And I myself spend most of my free time"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 772249.0,
      "end_time": 775352.0,
      "text": "making these science videos that I put on YouTube."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 775873.0,
      "end_time": 778830.0,
      "text": "I explain chemical equilibrium"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 778107.0,
      "end_time": 781587.0,
      "text": "using analogies to awkward middle school dances,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 781611.0,
      "end_time": 783317.0,
      "text": "and I talk about fuel cells"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 783341.0,
      "end_time": 786444.0,
      "text": "with stories about boys and girls at a summer camp."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 787506.0,
      "end_time": 790910.0,
      "text": "The feedback that I get is sometimes misspelled"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 790934.0,
      "end_time": 793770.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s often written in LOLcats,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 793101.0,
      "end_time": 794315.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 794339.0,
      "end_time": 800259.0,
      "text": "but nonetheless, it&#39;s so appreciative, so thankful"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 800283.0,
      "end_time": 806505.0,
      "text": "that I know this is the right way we should be communicating science."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 807333.0,
      "end_time": 810380.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s still so much work left to be done, though,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 810404.0,
      "end_time": 813642.0,
      "text": "and if you&#39;re involved with science in any way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 813666.0,
      "end_time": 815935.0,
      "text": "I urge you to join me."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 816356.0,
      "end_time": 821716.0,
      "text": "Pick up a camera, start to write a blog, whatever,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 821740.0,
      "end_time": 825168.0,
      "text": "but leave out the seriousness, leave out the jargon."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 825589.0,
      "end_time": 828960.0,
      "text": "Make me laugh. Make me care."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 828984.0,
      "end_time": 832539.0,
      "text": "Leave out those annoying details that nobody cares about"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 832563.0,
      "end_time": 834912.0,
      "text": "and just get to the point."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 836309.0,
      "end_time": 837492.0,
      "text": "How should you start?"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 838174.0,
      "end_time": 841886.0,
      "text": "Why don&#39;t you say, \"Listen, let me tell you a story.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 843323.0,
      "end_time": 844473.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    }
  ]
}